00:56:17.875 --> 00:56:19.208
Every one of you.

00:56:19.417 --> 00:56:22.667
You can change your hands now. You can use the left hand.

00:56:22.875 --> 00:56:25.875
Put the right hand towards Me.

00:56:26.709 --> 00:56:28.959
Keep your eyes shut and ask the question:

00:56:29.125 --> 00:56:33.667
“Mother, is this the breeze?”

00:56:38.709 --> 00:56:41.333
All of you should get it.

00:56:41.542 --> 00:56:44.500
Possible! Change your hands again if you want to.

00:56:44.709 --> 00:56:48.917
You go on changing and see if there’s a cool breeze coming out.

00:56:49.083 --> 00:56:52.041
It has to be cool breeze. First the heat will come out,

00:56:52.250 --> 00:56:55.458
so it’s a good sign that the heat is going out,

00:56:55.667 --> 00:57:00.083
all the heat with tension and all that is going out.

00:57:06.291 --> 00:57:09.166
It’s working out. It’s very subtle.

00:57:09.375 --> 00:57:12.000
We are moving from gross awareness

00:57:12.208 --> 00:57:14.875
to a subtler awareness of the roots.

00:57:15.041 --> 00:57:20.291
So naturally, one has to pay attention to it.

00:57:20.500 --> 00:57:23.041
Little in front, it is not at the back of the head

00:57:23.250 --> 00:57:26.667
but little bit in the front side.

00:57:26.875 --> 00:57:32.999
Try one after another and pay attention to it.

00:57:53.000 --> 00:57:56.000
Very hot today!

00:58:37.250 --> 00:58:41.542
Now, without opening the eyes, again put back hands towards Me

00:58:41.750 --> 00:58:43.542
like this,

00:58:43.750 --> 00:58:46.834
and see if there’s a cool breeze

00:58:47.000 --> 00:58:50.125
coming to your fingertips, to begin with.

00:58:50.333 --> 00:58:56.375
Just put both the hands and see if there’s a cool breeze.

00:59:00.291 --> 00:59:02.500
Ask again the question:

00:59:02.709 --> 00:59:07.834
“Is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?”

00:59:08.500 --> 00:59:14.917
Ask thrice. Means the Kundalini. Kundalini is the Holy Ghost.

