How is the lady?

00:59:21.709 --> 00:59:24.959
It’s all right. Don’t worry, she’ll be all right.

00:59:25.125 --> 00:59:30.166
She’ll be all right, don’t worry. Don’t worry, she’ll be all right.

00:59:30.625 --> 00:59:33.834
Don’t worry, she’ll be all right.

00:59:34.000 --> 00:59:36.875
She’ll be all right. Don’t worry, I’m looking after her.

00:59:37.041 --> 00:59:40.041
She’s come.

00:59:42.917 --> 00:59:45.917
She’ll be all right.

