01:01:25.500 --> 01:01:28.291
Don’t talk to them, don’t touch them,

01:01:28.500 --> 01:01:32.959
just start raising the Kundalini.

01:01:33.417 --> 01:01:35.959
Slowly, try to do it.

01:01:36.125 --> 01:01:39.250
Keep your eyes shut. We’ll work it out for you.

01:01:39.458 --> 01:01:42.125
Now, those who have come for the first time

01:01:42.333 --> 01:01:46.500
